body:
What is it? The Platform Engineering Chapter is one of several technical communities of practice within Cloud &amp; Edge. These “Chapters” are communities of people with similar competences and expertise, working on knowledge sharing and continuous development of our skills in line with market needs and the ambitions of the business through collaboration with Group SBUs and capability teams outside of CIS.
Why do I want it? The Platform Engineering Chapter will underpin capability development in P&amp;C through;
 Sales accelerators Skills Tracks Sand Pit Environments Hands on Exercises Technical Meetups  Where should I go next?  Getting Started
